title: Flip-Flop Sublinear Models for Graphs: Proof of Theorem 1
abstract: We prove that there is no class-dual for almost all sublinear models on graphs.
histories: Supplementary material for B. Jain. Flip-Flop Sublinear Models for Graphs, S+SSPR 2014
